  "body": "<!--NOTE: -->\r\n<!--- General questions should go to the discord chat instead of the issue tracker.-->\r\n\r\n**Describe the bug**\r\n\r\nOf about 42MB/day, seen in Ropsten nodes in the last 14 days. They run unstable without watchtower so don't update automatically. Versions run through this period:\r\n- 067edc40c4b15fc5558a0e442eeeb67bdb431738 from 07/28\r\n- b34abb7760e011d7ccbf72a9e0bcfa02140a99e3 from 08/03\r\n- v0.41.0 from 08/15\r\n\r\n\r\n![Screenshot from 2022-08-16 09-29-50](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/35266934/184823228-8a786efe-d5d0-4545-aa2b-2e976d3bfff5.png)\r\n![Screenshot from 2022-08-16 09-30-00](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/35266934/184823241-906d4ef5-2ff4-431a-91a5-ce66e8e54fb4.png)\r\n\r\nThis is also seen in Sepolia node\r\n\r\n![Screenshot from 2022-08-16 09-36-06](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/35266934/184823979-ef072b1c-f749-4e1a-a749-7507bb68b537.png)\r\n\r\n**Expected behavior**\r\n\r\nStable memory long term",
